    "The mapping of feature groups with functional groups helps to show the decision making process involved in scoring the essays.",
    "There are several datasets associated with AES tasks, but only a few are free and publicly available.",
    "In this section, we will discuss the popular datasets that have been used in recent AES research works.",
    "Table 8 shows the widely used datasets in AES.",
    "The ASAP and ASAP++ datasets are free and publicly available as well as the widely used datasets in recent years."
